## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all cultural nuances. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude perspectives from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of international business means that cultural perceptions and their impacts can evolve, potentially affecting the relevance of the findings over time.